should be consistent about ways of loading modules:

type/package -> default all

type/package/compiler -> default version, tag; specific compiler
type/package/version -> default compiler, tag; specific version
type/package/tag -> default compiler, version; specific tag

type/package/version/compiler -> default tag; specific version, compiler

type/package/version/compiler/tag -> specific all

type/package/compiler-gcc
type/package/version (standard)
